* 2012：「联合国海洋法会议@30」（{{lang|en|UNCLOS @ 30}}）<ref>{{cite web |url=https://unworldoceansday.org/un-world-oceans-day-2012/ |title=UN World Oceans Day 2012 |publisher=United Nations World Oceans Day}}</ref> — [[聯合國海洋法公約|聯合國海洋法公約]]
* 2013：「海洋与人民」（{{lang|en|Oceans & People}}）<ref>{{cite web |url=https://unworldoceansday.org/un-world-oceans-day-2013/ |title=UN World Oceans Day 2013 |publisher=United Nations World Oceans Day}}</ref>
* 2014：「众志成城，保护海洋」（{{lang|en|Ocean Sustainability: Together let's ensure oceans can sustain us into the future}}）<ref>{{cite web |url=https://unworldoceansday.org/un-world-oceans-day-2014 |title=UN World Oceans Day 2014 |publisher=United Nations World Oceans Day}}</ref>
* 2015：「健康的海洋，健康的地球」（{{lang|en|Healthy Oceans, Healthy Planet}}）<ref>{{cite web |url=https://unworldoceansday.org/un-world-oceans-day-2015 |title=UN World Oceans Day 2015 |publisher=United Nations World Oceans Day}}</ref>
* 2016：「健康的海洋，健康的地球」<ref>{{cite news |url=https://news.un.org/zh/story/2016/06/258222 |title=2016年世界海洋日：健康的海洋 健康的地球 |publisher=联合国新闻 |date=2016-06-07}}</ref>（{{lang|en|Healthy Oceans, Healthy Planet}}）<ref>{{cite web |url=https://unworldoceansday.org/un-world-oceans-day-2016 |title=UN World Oceans Day 2016 |publisher=United Nations World Oceans Day}}</ref>
* 2017：「我們的海洋，我們的未來」<ref>{{cite news |url=https://news.un.org/zh/story/2017/06/277122 |title=世界海洋日：联合国赞美海洋为人类做出的贡献 呼吁人们加倍珍惜和保护海洋 |publisher=联合国新闻 |date=2017-06-08}}</ref>（{{lang|en|Our Oceans, Our Future}}）<ref>{{cite web |url=https://unworldoceansday.org/un-world-oceans-day-2017 |title=UN World Oceans Day 2017 |publisher=United Nations World Oceans Day}}</ref> — 保護行動的重點放在鼓勵解決[[塑料污染|塑料污染]]和[[海洋廢棄物|海洋垃圾]]，為了一個更健康的海洋，和更美好的未來。 世界各地計劃舉辦數百場活動，包括這一周在[[紐約市|紐約市]]舉行第一次的{{link-en|聯合國海洋會議|The United Nations Ocean Conference}}。
* 2018：「清洁我们的海洋」<ref>{{cite news |url=https://news.un.org/zh/story/2018/06/1010561 |title=【专题报道】世界海洋日：保护海洋 向塑料污染宣战 |publisher=联合国新闻 |date=2018-06-08}}</ref>（{{lang|en|Clean our Ocean!}}）<ref>{{cite web |url=https://unworldoceansday.org/un-world-oceans-day-2018 |title=UN World Oceans Day 2018 |publisher=United Nations World Oceans Day}}</ref>
